data.description: Welcome Home!  Great School District.  This 5 bedroom homes features a lush master suite on the main level, 3 bedrooms upstairs and one on the lower level.  The 2 story foyers is flanked on the left by a separate dining room and invites you into a massive great room which is an incredible space for entertaining and allows flow directly into the kitchen and breakfast bar and breakfast area.  Need more space for man-cave or she-shed well take a journey down  to the finished basement with access to a walk out patio and also has a boat door with unfinished room that can be customized or used for storage.  From the deck off the kitchen there are views of the large fenced back yard and it over looks the lake.   How about that for fishing in your own backyard.  Schedule your showing today.
